-- MOVES-Martin Davies named Westchester Group's European unit CEO
-- 
-- Wed Oct 08, 2014 12:27PM EDT
-- None



Oct 8 (Reuters) - Agricultural asset manager Westchester Group Investment Management Inc said it appointed Martin Davies executive vice president and chief executive of Westchester Group of Europe Ltd.

Based in the UK, Davies will develop the company's direct farmland investment business in Europe, Westchester said in a statement. His appointment came into effect on Monday. Davies joins from Insight Investment, where he was head of farmland investments for the past five years.